# Windows

Run ALL terminal commands through Git Bash using the full path:

"C:\Program Files\Git\bin\bash.exe" -c 'your command here'

NEVER use PowerShell or cmd.exe directly. They will fail.

No Git Bash installed: stop and direct the user to https://gitforwindows.org
